	(1245,114,'Housing','Harlem spreads from 110th to 155th street, making it one of the largest neighborhoods in NYC. Due to the current renovations, Harlem continues to grow, adding yet another chapter to its extensive history.\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC is located in the heart of Harlem, conveniently placed by the 2,3,4,5, and 6 subway lines. DSS Services LLC has over 25 years of Real Estate experience, servicing its community and surrounding cities. Weather you reside in the Bronx, Brooklyn, or Staten Island – or are planning to move to one of the five boroughs – “We can satisfy all your real estate needs”. Right across the street from Mt Morris Park, DSS Services LLC is rapidly growing and our professional staff has risen to the high demands that face fellow New Yorkers today. We are the ultimate one stop shop for all your professional, personal, and financial needs, including renting, selling, buying and much more.'),
	(1246,114,'Restaurants','With its many historic landmarks; including The Apollo Theater, 125th street, and the Polo Grounds, the richness of Harlem continues to drive businessman, educators, and tourist to its’ center. Harlem also features some of the best soul food around; like Silvia\\\'s, Spoonbread, and much more. So full of history, it is now; “the place to be”.'),
