	(45,1,'2014-05-16 13:48:15','2014-05-16 13:48:15','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<label>Name*:</label>[text* your-name]\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<label>Email*:</label>[email* your-email]\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<label>Phone:</label>[tel tel-456]\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"text\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			Or send an email directly to: <a href=\"mailto:info@dssserv.com\">info@dssserv.com</a>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n	<label>How Can We Help You*:</label>\r\n	[textarea* textarea-69]\r\n	<div class=\"text\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">Marked Fields are Mandatory!</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-3\">[submit \"Send\"]</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\n[your-name] is interested in [_post_title]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\n\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[textarea-69]\r\n\r\nApartment URL [_post_url]\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on DSS Services (http://localhost:8888/dssserv)\njskinner@spidadesign.com\n\n\n\n\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on DSS Services (http://localhost:8888/dssserv)\n[your-email]\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nPlease fill the required field.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nNumber format seems invalid.\nThis number is too small.\nThis number is too large.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nURL seems invalid.\nTelephone number seems invalid.\nYour answer is not correct.\nDate format seems invalid.\nThis date is too early.\nThis date is too late.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.','Property Information','','publish','open','open','','property-information','','','2014-05-27 19:37:41','2014-05-27 19:37:41','',0,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=45',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),
	(122,1,'2014-06-09 15:10:04','2014-06-09 15:10:04','Frank Sinatra once said “If I could make it here, I could make it anywhere”, New York City is a very fast paced city full of diversity. With so many cultures, races, and backgrounds stemming from Chinatown to Washington Heights, New York has proven to not just be the melting pot of the country, but of the world. However, none demonstrates to be livelier than Harlem.','NYC & Harlem Real Estate, Condos and Homes','','inherit','open','open','','114-autosave-v1','','','2014-06-09 15:10:04','2014-06-09 15:10:04','',114,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/114-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(123,1,'2014-06-09 15:10:09','2014-06-09 15:10:09','Frank Sinatra once said “If I could make it here, I could make it anywhere”, New York City is a very fast paced city full of diversity. With so many cultures, races, and backgrounds stemming from Chinatown to Washington Heights, New York has proven to not just be the melting pot of the country, but of the world. However, none demonstrates to be livelier than Harlem.','NYC & Harlem Real Estate, Condos and Homes','','inherit','open','open','','114-revision-v1','','','2014-06-09 15:10:09','2014-06-09 15:10:09','',114,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/114-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(5,1,'2014-04-29 20:33:00','2014-04-29 20:33:00','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce in ante dolor. Sed vestibulum hendrerit nisl, in aliquam ipsum pretium semper. Fusce tincidunt dui condimentum risus lacinia ornare. In eget odio ut elit suscipit pharetra. Curabitur a dolor aliquam, commodo purus sed, tristique quam. Aliquam porttitor eleifend blandit. Morbi lacinia nisl urna, ac egestas arcu venenatis sed.\r\n\r\nProin non porta massa, in ornare felis. Etiam condimentum scelerisque pellentesque. Phasellus euismod rutrum erat, at posuere odio malesuada vel. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Vestibulum vestibulum vitae dolor quis tempor. Duis auctor sed odio at volutpat.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nVestibulum vestibulum vitae dolor quis tempor. Duis auctor sed odio at volutpat. Phasellus ac metus congue purus viverra auctor ut id felis. Aliquam cursus vestibulum eros sit amet iaculis.\r\n\r\nProin euismod justo libero, a posuere velit varius vel. Quisque turpis leo, gravida vel massa sed, volutpat viverra est. Nulla sodales lorem in dolor lobortis consequat. Maecenas consequat, odio hendrerit ultricies convallis, ligula metus elementum purus, nec tempor turpis erat in purus. Sed in dui in purus tincidunt porta. Mauris suscipit massa odio. Curabitur rutrum felis sed mattis bibendum. Suspendisse semper aliquam blandit. Cras tempor viverra tellus non gravida. Nullam semper luctus quam eu rutrum. In quis sapien orci.\r\n\r\n</div>','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-05-23 20:59:16','2014-05-23 20:59:16','',0,'http://spidadesign.us/dssserv/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),
