	(46,1,'2014-05-19 15:20:58','2014-05-19 15:20:58','<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h2>Do you want to rent your apartment?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">A good way to put your apartment up for rent is by advertising it in an ad or newspaper. A virtual tour of the apartment can provide a better visual and generate more prospective clients. This can enhance the marketing of the property. By taking pictures of selected areas of the apartment, it can also be a photo layout of the property. The apartment listing will be immediately available to the entire brokerage community, including all of Manhattan’s real estate board of New York and their cooperating brokers and their renters.</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">When it comes down to renting an apartment, time management is important. Apartments have to get rented as soon as possible. DSS Services LLC has a list of pre qualified renters. Agents are committed to getting the job done to the highest level of personal customer service. We provide customers with up to date comparables of currently available properties. We are highly experienced in renting apartments. An agent will interact with you to negotiate a price and to figure out a timely approval to secure the occupancy of your apartment. Why wait, Call us now!</div>','Rentals','','publish','open','open','','rentals','','','2014-06-19 18:46:07','2014-06-19 18:46:07','',0,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/?page_id=46',0,'page','',0),
