	(52,1,'2014-05-19 15:36:25','2014-05-19 15:36:25','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC has a complete line of insurance products for those seeking the ultimate insurance in customer satisfaction and professionalism. We offer extensive amounts of coverage for Life, Health, Auto, Home, and Commercial/Business. Our extraordinarily wide range of business goes from a single person to a company with revenues in the millions. No task is too big or too small!\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC makes meeting your insurance needs an experience you will never forget! Due to the seriousness of getting insurance in today\'s society, we will work with you and depict every single last detail to customize your insurance needs for the maximum amount of coverage with the minimal costs.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC also offers defensive driving courses to help save 10% on your auto insurance premiums or reduce points off of your license. Space is limited so call today to reserve your space.\r\n\r\nDSS Services LLC works with an extensive amount of insurance companies to provide the necessary coverage for all of your insurance needs. Please contact us today for your free quote!\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Apartment Building</li>\r\n	<li>Mold and Fungus</li>\r\n	<li>Lead Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Auto Personal</li>\r\n	<li>Home Renters, Condos and Apartments</li>\r\n	<li>Fire</li>\r\n	<li>All types of insurance</li>\r\n	<li> Commercial Business</li>\r\n	<li>Professional Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Insurance','','publish','open','open','','insurance','','','2014-05-27 18:34:01','2014-05-27 18:34:01','',0,'http://localhost:8888/dssserv/?page_id=52',0,'page','',0),
